{"tid":383534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[返支那啦你]旅居日本評立法　國歌填詞人侄女稱深受感動","createTime":"2017-09-01T14:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T02:27:21.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1aefc7f6880a6d3d08f8149282e2cb22cfea0e","tid":383534,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返支那啦你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170901/s00004/1504272596106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170901%2Fs00004%2F1504272596106&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b1da0eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170901%2Fs00004%2F1504272596106&h=856df774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170901/s00004/1504272596106</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170901/s00004/68d638c69d2a3bb264ab95d121be12b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170901%2Fs00004%2F68d638c69d2a3bb264ab95d121be12b6.jpg&h=28d22eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會今日通過《中華人民共和國國歌法》，國歌《義勇軍進行曲》的填詞人田漢，其侄女田偉稱對立法非常感動。<br />\n<br />\n田偉現旅居日本，早年於日本一直向外國宣揚國歌，並傳遞國歌內的中國力量。田偉更成立文化研究會、受邀演唱國歌，更自費出版《國歌80周年》書籍。今年7月，更於日本舉辦了「田漢&middot;聶耳的故事」音樂會，以國歌開場。<br />\n<br />\n田偉認為，《國歌法》鼓勵人民唱國歌，令她大受鼓舞，並稱會繼續為研究和傳唱國歌。"},{"pid":"bbeb4cbc3aa08f0f2b7975d2e16f2408b3fb60d2","tid":383534,"uid":83582,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"點解佢唔返支那住?????"},{"pid":"2c3191c43c4cb00295ab842dc01d6b0a47fec03c","tid":383534,"uid":67551,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"田漢點死？<im